Czech Ministry Suspends Sazka’s Lottery Licence, CT24 Reports

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-05-09T10:52:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/czech-ministry-suspends-sazka-s-lottery-licence-ct24-reports.html
The Czech  Finance Ministry  suspended
Sazka AS’s lottery license,  CT24  reported, without saying where
it got the information.  Ministry spokesman Jakub Haase declined to comment when
contacted by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story: Lenka Ponikelska in
Prague   lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  